when she came out to the main entrance of the building."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Now I'm curious about what exactly kept her so long."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I was also a bit worried, so I just asked her directly."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[54-nb]Ah, erhm you see... the boss was showing me some of his kitchen skills."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I see. It's her we're talking about, so I bet she was eager to learn too."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I imagine her cooking will eventually reach the owner's level someday."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["If that's all it was then I ought to be supporting her too."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I mean, if her cooking skills improve, the one who'll benefit"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["the most in the end is gonna be me."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["While trying to hide such naughty thoughts, I told her"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["[I'll come pick you up on days you stay late, so feel free to get more practice in]."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[54-nb]...Thanks. I really will take you up on that."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["She laughed and smiled a bit apologetically."]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[408,408,0]},{"code":357,"indent":0,"parameters":["TRP_SkitMZ","end","スキット終了",{"noAnimatio